summary: I started watching Dan and Phil like,2014-2015? I only had a huge crush for Dan, I thought he was cute, his dimples, his voice,...
body:
My Story of Developing a Crush on Phil:

I started watching Dan and Phil like,2014-2015? I only had a huge crush for Dan, I thought he was cute, his dimples, his voice, his eyes, his style (I’m just rambling, everything is perfect about Dan!)

For 3-4 years I only had a thing for Dan. He was basically what I basically looked for in a guy: funny, cute, memey, caring, adorable, and very inappropriate 😂

As the 3-4 years passed, I continued watching Dan and Phil. Phil; quite quirky, innocent (yeah sure lol), funny, always eating, and always acted super adorable. I thought his personality was perfect, but I just never liked how he looked. My dumb self, I for the most part, go based off looks and only sometimes personality (Reason why I have an actual liking to the guys that bully me at school. But that’s a whole another stupid ass story..) Phil’s personality caught me to the extent of wanting to be his very close friend but not have a crush on him.

If my information is correct, In March of 2018, Phil put his hair into a quiff and I really didn’t think much of it other than like the whole fandom {FOREHEAD DJSISJD} you know.

I don’t know when these pictures were released but I found them through starting up my DNP Tumblr, I literally just in the moment fell in love with Phil.

These two pictures converted me from just wanted to be his friend, to actually a huge crush. I still have a huge crush on Dan, (Of course ;3)

Phil really came up on me quick with all his other pictures after that, for some reason I feel like it’s just his confidence in showing off and his just structure of his face with more of his forehead but I really don’t know..

But ending the story now, I now gave a crush on both Dan and Phil.. Woooooooooowwieeeeee, but yeah I l love them both they are perfect and ye ❤️ hopefully this wasn’t really boring but it’s a factual story haha but ye :3 cyaaaa laterrrrrr ~ Kym 💕

{ Cute Filler Pic Of My Bois }

@danielhowell @amazingphil

So the theme of the year In the Phandom has been ‘giving the people what they want’. So, what if Dan and Phil asked us for ideas for the calendar. It would be the perfect end to the ‘giving the people what they want’ year. i’m just saying maybe its an idea
